(9, 1, '2017-02-22 02:30:50', '2017-02-22 02:30:50', '<div class=" et_pb_row et_pb_row_1 et_pb_gutters2">\r\n<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_2 et_pb_column_1">\r\n<div id="toptext" class="et_pb_promo et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_cta_1 et_pb_no_bg">\r\n<div class="et_pb_promo_description">\r\n<h2>FINAL STEP:  INSTALL TAS FOR DT PRO / GAIN</h2>\r\nThis page will guide you through how to successfully install TAS Indicators on your computer for use on the DT Pro / Gain platform.\r\n\r\n<em>NOTE: An active <strong>membership</strong> is required for TAS products to wo</em>rk.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_2 et_pb_column_2"></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=" et_pb_row et_pb_row_2">\r\n<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_4_4 et_pb_column_3">\r\n<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_text_0">\r\n<h4><strong>PART 1:  INSTALL TAS INDICATORS SOFTWARE</strong></h4>\r\nStart by shutting down your platform. Then, install the TAS Indicators software on your computer by clicking the button below and following the on-screen instructions (i.e. next, proceed, ok, etc). Most relative new computers should install the “64-Bit” version of the software.\r\n\r\n<strong>* IMPORTANT NOTE:</strong>  During installation, you may be prompted to install Windows Visual C++. These are required Windows files to run the software and you should proceed. Additionally, you may prompted to “repair” or “update” the the existing version that you have and if so, please choose the repair option. A reboot may be required thereafter.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<a href="http://tasmarketprofile.com/TASIndicatorsOEC64.exe" target="_blank">Install 64-Bit Version</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<a href="http://tasmarketprofile.com/TASIndicatorsOEC32.exe" target="_blank">Install 32-Bit Version</a>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h4><strong>PART 2: LOGIN TO THE TAS LAUNCH PAD (REQUIRED)</strong></h4>\r\nWhen using the