eft et_pb_text_1">\r\n\r\n<strong>INSTALLING TO THE CORRECT MT4 DIRECTORY:</strong>  Make sure your MetaTrader platform links to the right installation directory folder. Since MetaTrader is used by many brokerage firms, the installation files may install in different folders depending on your MT4 provider firm and the default install file may not be correct. View the video at the right for how to ensure your platform is links correctly.\r\n\r\n<strong>Then proceed to Part 2 of the instructions below.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_2 et_pb_column_5">\r\n<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_video et_pb_video_0">\r\n<div class="et_pb_video_box">\r\n<div class="wistia_responsive_padding">\r\n<div class="wistia_responsive_wrapper">\r\n<div class="wistia_video_foam_dummy" data-source-container-id=""></div>\r\n<iframe class="wistia_embed" title="Wistia video player" src="http://fast.wistia.net/embed/iframe/r54d27ye90?videoFoam=true" name="wistia_embed" width="510" height="359" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="et_pb_row et_pb_row_4 et_pb_row_3-4_1-4">\r\n<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_3_4 et_pb_column_6">\r\n<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_text_2">\r\n<h4><strong>PART 2: LOGIN TO THE TAS LAUNCH PAD (REQUIRED)</strong></h4>\r\nWhen using the TAS Indicators on your charting platform, you must be logged into our required TAS Launch Pad program. Locate the TAS “triangle” shortcut on your desktop that says “TAS Launch Pad” (see image at right), then click it and you’ll be prompted to enter your login details. You should have received these via a welcome email when joining.\r\n\r\n<strong>* IMPORTANT NOTE:</strong>  After you have successfully logged in, you may minimize the Launch Pad program window while using the indicators but you should avoid closing it. There is a convenient option to “Remember Me” so the program retains your credentials for future login efforts. If you should accidentally logout or close the program, simply login again.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_4 et_pb_column_7"><img src="http://tasmarketprofile.com//wp-content/uploads/2016/12/TAS_Launch_Pad_desktop_icon.png" alt="" /></div>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=" et_pb_row et_pb_row_5">\r\n<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_2 et_pb_column_8">\r\n<div class="et_pb_text et_pb_module et_pb_bg_layout_light et_pb_text_align_left et_pb_text_3">\r\n<h4><strong>PART 3:  INSERT INDICATORS ON THE CHART (VIDEO)</strong></h4>\r\nAfter you have successfully installed the indicators and logged into the TAS Launch Pad, you can start your charting platform. View the short video to the right for a quick tutorial on how to insert the indicators on your chart.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="et_pb_column et_pb_column_1_2 et_pb_column_9">\r\n<div class="et_pb_module et_pb_video et_pb_video_1">\r\n<div class="et_pb_video_box">\r\n<div class="wistia_responsive_padding">\r\n<div class="wistia_responsive_wrapper">\r\n<div class="wistia_video_foam_dummy" data-source-container-id=""></div>\r\n<iframe class="wistia_embed" title="Wistia video player" src="http://fast.wistia.net/embed/iframe/k9daejcjxa?videoFoam=true" name="wistia_embed" width="510" height="359" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" data-mce-fragment="1"></iframe>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Install for MetaTrader', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '26-revision-v1', '', '', '2017-02-22 02:48:46', '2017-02-22 02:48:46', '', 26, 'http://tasboxes.com/26-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
